BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:XMjvWdhQcflOM4GxvkB-o
SUMMARY:Mary Jane
DTSTAMP:20260326T160825Z
DTSTART:20260328T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:Poignantly humorous and deeply cathartic\, this semi-autobiogra
	phical drama by Tony-nominated playwright Amy Herzog is a love letter to c
